=============================
       Linux, OS-X, BSD
=============================

Build:
------

Start by configuring the build folder:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake <root path of cppmyth>

Then build the lib:

make


Generate the documentation:
---------------------------

doxygen <root path of cppmyth>/docs/doxygen-user.cfg
doxygen <root path of cppmyth>/docs/doxygen-dev.cfg
